# =============================================================================
# .gitignore — Torin Gunnell Digital
# Enforces CLAUDE.md's hard rule: NO media files in Git. Photos/clips → R2,
# full films → Vimeo. Only code + tiny static assets (logo SVG, favicons) belong.
# =============================================================================

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
.vscode/
.idea/

# Dependencies (not needed for this plain static build, but just in case)
node_modules/

# --- MEDIA: never commit (CLAUDE.md §2, §10) ---
# Video
*.mp4
*.mov
*.webm
*.m4v
*.avi
# Wedding photos / large rasters (these live on Cloudflare R2, not Git)
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.png
*.webp
*.avif
*.psd
*.tif
*.tiff
*.raw

# Allow ONLY the small static brand assets that belong in the repo:
!favicon-16.png
!favicon-32.png
!favicon-48.png
!apple-touch-icon.png
!images/social.jpg
# (SVGs are not ignored — logo/icon SVGs are welcome.)
